00:17:58.320 --> 00:18:01.020
So we have a rapid process
improvement workshop

00:18:01.020 --> 00:18:04.020
that's going to be
three to five days, say.

00:18:04.020 --> 00:18:05.790
And it starts by
understanding what

00:18:05.790 --> 00:18:07.740
is important to improve
in the enterprise.

00:18:07.740 --> 00:18:10.240
And there's always more
to improve than resources.

00:18:10.240 --> 00:18:12.120
So you do some kind
of Pareto chart.

00:18:12.120 --> 00:18:15.150
We've done that informally
with this kind of thing we had,

00:18:15.150 --> 00:18:18.490
which was, what were the big
bottlenecks you had to address?

00:18:18.490 --> 00:18:20.040
So you pick some target.

00:18:20.040 --> 00:18:23.280
You make a strategic choice on
what you're going to improve.

00:18:23.280 --> 00:18:25.620
And then you may take three
months or so to get ready.

00:18:25.620 --> 00:18:27.120
You have to go out
and get the data.

00:18:27.120 --> 00:18:28.770
You have to figure out who
are the right stakeholders.

00:18:28.770 --> 00:18:31.710
You have to plan it so the
stakeholders can be available.

00:18:31.710 --> 00:18:34.860
You're going to pour a lot
of resources in for one week.

00:18:34.860 --> 00:18:36.750
But you'll probably pour
a lot less resources

00:18:36.750 --> 00:18:39.195
than if you try to stretch
it over six months to a year.

00:18:39.195 --> 00:18:41.820
PROFESSOR: And the agreement has
to be that the stakeholders do

00:18:41.820 --> 00:18:44.340
not leave the room,
turn off cell phones,

00:18:44.340 --> 00:18:47.058
and they're cloistered
for the whole time.

00:18:47.058 --> 00:18:47.850
EARLL MURMAN: Yeah.

00:18:47.850 --> 00:18:50.023
And they don't arrive late,
and they don't go back

00:18:50.023 --> 00:18:50.940
to some other meeting.

00:18:50.940 --> 00:18:52.980
That's it.

00:18:52.980 --> 00:18:55.970
And that's why you need
this top level support.

00:18:55.970 --> 00:18:59.060
OK, then that group
is given a charter.

00:18:59.060 --> 00:19:00.980
And they're given the
resources they need

00:19:00.980 --> 00:19:02.690
