00:19:35.600 --> 00:19:37.100
You made a mistake somewhere.

00:19:37.100 --> 00:19:38.210
Training is a typical one.

00:19:38.210 --> 00:19:39.835
You didn't get people
trained properly,

00:19:39.835 --> 00:19:40.950
or something like that.

00:19:40.950 --> 00:19:43.430
And so you may have to
do some follow-up action.

00:19:43.430 --> 00:19:47.420
And then you feed that back in
